{"title_page": "Badhan, Sanaag", "text_new": "{{pp-protected|small=yes}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!--See the Table at Infobox settlement for all fields and descriptions of usage-->\n<!-- Basic info  ---------------->| official_name                   = Badhan\n| native_name                     = Baran\n| other_name                      = '''\u0628\u0631\u0646'''\n| settlement_type                 = Town\n| image_skyline                   = Badhan overview.jpg\n| imagesize                       = 250px\n| image_caption                   = Badhan overview\n| image_flag                      = \n| flag_size                       = \n| image_seal                      = \n| seal_size                       = \n| image_shield                    = \n| shield_size                     = \n| image_blank_emblem              = \n| blank_emblem_type               = \n| blank_emblem_size               = \n| nickname                        = \n| motto                           = <!-- images and maps  ----------->\n| image_map                       = \n| mapsize                         = \n| map_caption                     = \n| image_map1                      = \n| mapsize1                        = \n| map_caption1                    = \n| pushpin_map                     = Somaliland#Somalia#Africa\n| pushpin_label_position          = bottom\n| pushpin_mapsize                 = 250\n| pushpin_map_caption             = Location in Somaliland\n<!-- Location ------------------>| coordinates                     = {{coord|10|42|50|N|48|20|5|E|region:SO|display=inline}}\n<!-- General information  --------------->| subdivision_type                = [[Country]]\n| subdivision_name                = {{flag|Somalia}}\n| subdivision_type1               = [[Administrative divisions of Somaliland|Region]]\n| subdivision_type2               = [[Administrative divisions of Somaliland|District]]\n| subdivision_type3               = \n| subdivision_type4               = \n| subdivision_name1           